OL,3,CPope blesses Sagrada Familia's new
OL,4,Ctower in firework-lit ceremony
OL,6,FThe Pope has celebrated the Sagrada
OL,7,FFamilia Basilica as a masterpiece of
OL,8,F"stones, colours and light" as he
OL,9,Fmarked 100 years since the passing of
OL,10,Fits architect, Antoni Gaudi.
OL,12,FPope Leo XIV visited the Barcelona
OL,13,Fchurch as part of his week-long trip
OL,14,Fto Spain - the first by a pontiff in
OL,15,F15 years - and praised the new Tower
OL,16,Fof Jesus Christ in a ceremony attended
OL,17,Fby around 120,000 people.
