OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781201469
OL,3,CPope blesses Sagrada Familia's new
OL,4,Ctower in firework-lit ceremony
OL,6,FSpeaking in Catalan and Spanish, Leo
OL,7,Fblessed the tower and its illuminated
OL,8,Fceramic cross from outside the
OL,9,Fbasilica, surrounded by bishops
OL,10,Fcraning their mitre-capped heads to
OL,11,Flook up.
OL,13,FThe completion of the tower, the
OL,14,Ftallest of 18 in the temple, means the
OL,15,Fbasilica has now reached its full
OL,16,Fheight of 172.5 metres, making it not
OL,17,Fonly the world's tallest church but
OL,18,FBarcelona's tallest building.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
