PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781201469
OL,3,CPope blesses Sagrada Familia's new
OL,4,Ctower in firework-lit ceremony
OL,6,FAn angelic boy's choir sang as a
OL,7,Fspectacular light show lit up the
OL,8,Fbasilica's stained glass windows from
OL,9,Fthe inside and fireworks shot off its
OL,10,Ffacade to mark the occasion.
OL,12,F"We are all the living stones of this
OL,13,Fedifice," Leo said from the altar of
OL,14,Fthe basilica, with Spanish King Felipe
OL,15,FVI and Queen Letizia sitting to his
OL,16,Fside.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@IO]
