PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781201469
OL,3,CPope blesses Sagrada Familia's new
OL,4,Ctower in firework-lit ceremony
OL,6,F"Much more than a monument, the
OL,7,FBasilica of the Sagrada Familia
OL,8,Fremains a work in progress today,
OL,9,Freminding us that the Christian life
OL,10,Fis always a journey, because it is a
OL,11,Fproject that God is carrying out," the
OL,12,FPope continued.
OL,14,FBefore the service, Leo lit a candle
OL,15,Fand prayed at the tomb of Gaudi.
OL,17,FThe Sagrada Familia was visited by 4.9
OL,18,Fmillion people last year, with entry
OL,19,Ffees contributing towards its ongoing
OL,20,Fconstruction.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@bO]wD@_rt
