OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781201469
OL,3,CPope blesses Sagrada Familia's new
OL,4,Ctower in firework-lit ceremony
OL,6,FHistorian Monica Santin, who leads
OL,7,Ftours of the basilica, said that in
OL,8,Fdesigning Sagrada Familia, Gaudi was
OL,9,Fguided by two books: the Gospels and
OL,10,Fnature.
OL,12,F"The way he lets in the natural light
OL,13,Fis also an invitation to the Christian
OL,14,Fmystery," she said, citing the three
OL,15,Ffacades depicting Christ's birth,
OL,16,Fdeath and glory.
OL,18,F"And when you enter inside, it is all
OL,19,Flight," Santin said.
