OL,3,CPope blesses Sagrada Familia's new
OL,4,Ctower in firework-lit ceremony
OL,6,F"What is that the symbol of? We can't
OL,7,Fsee God, but we perceive his light all
OL,8,Faround us. I think that is how you can
OL,9,Fread this message, and it is
OL,10,Ffascinating."
